  <div class="ProfileHeaderCard">
  <h1 class="ProfileHeaderCard-name">
    <a href="/hfoneill" class="ProfileHeaderCard-nameLink u-textInheritColor js-nav">Hannah O'Neill</a>

  <h2 class="ProfileHeaderCard-screenname u-inlineBlock u-dir" dir="ltr">
    <a class="ProfileHeaderCard-screennameLink u-linkComplex js-nav" href="/hfoneill">

    </a>
  </h2>

  

      <p class="ProfileHeaderCard-bio u-dir" dir="ltr">Lab &amp; Coop Deputy Leader and Cabinet lead for healthier and stronger communities, MK Council. PPC for MK South. Hate crime and equalities campaigner.</p>

<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">On my way to Milton Keynes South to join Labour's Parliamentary candidate <a href="/hfoneill" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="891940824"><s>@</s><b>hfoneill</b></a> and <a href="/MKLabourParty" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="118488277"><s>@</s><b>MKLabourParty</b></a> and <a href="/SELabour" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="1001454344"><s>@</s><b>SELabour</b></a>
volunteers to campaign to <a href="/hashtag/StopToryPoliceCuts?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>StopToryPoliceCuts</b></a> and for a Labour Government <a href="/hashtag/ForTheManyNotTheFew?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>ForTheManyNotTheFew</b></a><a href="https://t.co/DU9WtBvRmA" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/uklabour/status/967328763179450370" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/uklabour/status/967328763179450370"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/uklabour/statu</span><span class="invisible">s/967328763179450370</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

          <div class="QuoteTweet-text tweet-text u-dir" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="2" dir="ltr">Its Hate Crime Awareness Week next week!Go to <span rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="http://www.hatecrimenetwork.org.uk" class="twitter-timeline-link" target="_blank" title="http://www.hatecrimenetwork.org.uk"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">http://www.</span><span class="js-display-url">hatecrimenetwork.org.uk</span><span class="invisible"></span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></span> for details on getting involved! <span data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>WeStandTogether</b></span> <span data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>EverydayHateCrime</b></span></div>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">The arguments against the Human Rights Act are coming. They will be false<a href="http://t.co/3U5GuZdqAz" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="http://gu.com/p/48phz" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="http://gu.com/p/48phz"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="js-display-url">gu.com/p/48phz</span><span class="invisible"></span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
